text: Katerina Anastasiou (born 22 January 1973) is a Greek cross-country skier. She competed in the women's 5 kilometre classical at the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Greek female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Greece Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
